I noticed some folks are coming to this closed issue report problems they are facing, I'd suggest to open a new issue to individually address each problem if there is not already one opened.

@ngaloppo apparently there is a bug in the PYPI package so one alternative to solve this problem while it's not replaced for a working wheel is to download a nightly build.

body:
I noticed some folks are coming to this closed issue report problems they are facing, I'd suggest to open a new issue to individually address each problem if there is not already one opened.

@ngaloppo apparently there is a bug in the PYPI package so one alternative to solve this problem while it's not replaced for a working wheel is to download a [nightly build](http://ci.tensorflow.org/view/Nightly/job/nightly-win/92/).
